A list of INTERIOR POINTS may be given.
Every POINT will become a vertex of the tetrahedrization
The distance to the neighboring vertices will be
inferior to the WISHED DISTANCES given.

Example:  P1; P2;  {The INTERIOR POINTS}
          1; 2.5;  {The WISHED DISTANCES around}
Create a tetrahedrization with
edges from P1 at a distance < 1
edges from P2 at a distance < 2.5
